  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Create a new FormBuilder instanece on Rails 3]]></title>
    <link href="http://plum.iodot.org/blog/2012/04/12/new-formbuilder-instanece-on-rails-3/"/>
    <updated>2012-04-12T14:28:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://plum.iodot.org/blog/2012/04/12/new-formbuilder-instanece-on-rails-3</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>As on rails 2 we can create a new <code>ActionView::Helpers::FormBuilder</code>
instance with</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="no">ActionView</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Helpers</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">FormBuilder</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">new</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="ss">:foobar</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="vi">@foobar</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="vi">@template</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">{},</span> <span class="nb">proc</span><span class="p">{})</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>But on rails 3 this becomes</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="no">ActionView</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Helpers</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">FormBuilder</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">new</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="ss">:foobar</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="vi">@foobar</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">this</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">{},</span> <span class="nb">proc</span><span class="p">{})</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Just take a note.</p>
]]></content>
